    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been treated with the utmost care since it was new. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like shine with no chips, scratches, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and smells brand new. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records available. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor, offering a tight, responsive, and quiet ride. This is a rare opportunity to own a pre-owned vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 49500.0,
