    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes an optimal balance between performance and value. This unit exhibits a refined exterior and a well-preserved cabin, reflecting a history of consistent care and mechanical integrity. Its sophisticated engineering ensures a reliable and engaging driving experience, making it a premier choice for the discerning motorist seeking quality without compromise.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a reliable, great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. Everything runs smoothly, the interior is super comfy, and I've kept up with all the maintenance. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example has been properly sorted for the enthusiast, with the critical VANOS unit recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The naturally aspirated power delivery is sharpened by individual throttle bodies, while a limited-slip differential provides predictable torque bias through the apex. It sits on a refreshed suspension with Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining excellent damping characteristics without sacrificing compliance. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight and the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that balances luxury with everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Slate Grey Metallic that retains a deep gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, the body remains straight and free of any major dings. The alloy wheels are in great shape, showing only very light curbing on the passenger side. Inside, the charcoal leather interior has been kept in impressive condition. The driver\u2019s seat shows light bolster wear consistent with regular use, but the upholstery throughout is free of rips or odors. All electronic components, including the touchscreen infotainment, heated seats, and sunroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine idles quietly, and the transmission provides smooth, confident shifts. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and a complete folder of maintenance receipts, offering you full transparency into its history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its well-documented maintenance history and consistent performance. The exterior retains a professional luster, while the cabin offers a sophisticated environment for both driver and passengers. This selection represents an optimal balance of value and enduring quality, meticulously prepared for the discerning motorist who demands reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable ride! It\u2019s in great shape and has been really well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go without any fuss. It drives super smoothly and still looks fantastic on the road. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the pavement today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a precise steering rack. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping are dialed in for peak performance. A turn-key enthusiast machine with exceptional engine harmonics and lateral grip.",
